### Obtener alertas de stock bajo (Low Stock)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/inventory/alerts/low-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Consultar stock de un producto por ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Reponer stock (Restock) - Misma funcionalidad que en products.http
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/products/1/restock
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "quantity": 50
}
